{
    "poem_title": "La Maxime",
    "author": "Germain Nouveau",
    "structure": "suite périodique",
    "year": "1922",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "La Rochefoucauld dit, Madame,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Qu’on ne doit pas parler de soi,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Ni ?… ni ?… de ?… de ?… sa ?… sa ?… sa femme.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Alors, ma conduite est infâme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Voyez, je ne fais que ça, moi.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "La Rochefoucauld dit, Madame,\nQu’on ne doit pas parler de soi,\nNi ?… ni ?… de ?… de ?… sa ?… sa ?… sa femme.\nAlors, ma conduite est infâme,\nVoyez, je ne fais que ça, moi."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Je me moque de sa maxime.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Comme un fœtus dans un bocal,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "J’enferme mon « moi » dans ma rime,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Ce bon « moi » dont me fait un crime",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Le sévère Blaise Pascal.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je me moque de sa maxime.\nComme un fœtus dans un bocal,\nJ’enferme mon « moi » dans ma rime,\nCe bon « moi » dont me fait un crime\nLe sévère Blaise Pascal."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Or, ce ne serait rien encore,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "On excuse un… maudit travers ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Mais j’enferme Toi que j’adore",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Sur l’autel que mon souffle dore",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Au Temple bâti par mes vers ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Or, ce ne serait rien encore,\nOn excuse un… maudit travers ;\nMais j’enferme Toi que j’adore\nSur l’autel que mon souffle dore\nAu Temple bâti par mes vers ;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Sous les plafonds de mon Poëme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Sur mes tapis égyptiens,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Dans des flots d’encens, moi qui T’aime,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Je me couche auprès de Toi-même",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Comme auprès du Sphinx des Anciens ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sous les plafonds de mon Poëme,\nSur mes tapis égyptiens,\nDans des flots d’encens, moi qui T’aime,\nJe me couche auprès de Toi-même\nComme auprès du Sphinx des Anciens ;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Tel qu’un Faust prenant pour fétiche",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "L’un des coins brodés de tes bas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Je Te suis dans chaque hémistiche",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Où Tu bondis comme une biche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "La Biche-Femme des Sabbats ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tel qu’un Faust prenant pour fétiche\nL’un des coins brodés de tes bas,\nJe Te suis dans chaque hémistiche\nOù Tu bondis comme une biche,\nLa Biche-Femme des Sabbats ;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Comme pour la Sibylle à Cumes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Mon quatrain Te sert de trépied,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Où, dans un vacarme d’enclumes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Je m’abattrai, couvert d’écumes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Pour baiser le bout de ton pied ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Comme pour la Sibylle à Cumes,\nMon quatrain Te sert de trépied,\nOù, dans un vacarme d’enclumes,\nJe m’abattrai, couvert d’écumes,\nPour baiser le bout de ton pied ;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "À chaque endroit de la césure,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "D’un bout de rythme à l’autre bout,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Tu règnes avec grâce et sûre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "De remplir toute la mesure,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Assise, couchée, ou debout.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "À chaque endroit de la césure,\nD’un bout de rythme à l’autre bout,\nTu règnes avec grâce et sûre\nDe remplir toute la mesure,\nAssise, couchée, ou debout."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Eh, bien ! j’ai tort, je le confesse :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "On doit, jaloux de sa maison,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "N’en parler pas plus qu’à la messe ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Maxime pleine de sagesse !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "J’ai tort, sans doute… et j’ai raison.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Eh, bien ! j’ai tort, je le confesse :\nOn doit, jaloux de sa maison,\nN’en parler pas plus qu’à la messe ;\nMaxime pleine de sagesse !\nJ’ai tort, sans doute… et j’ai raison."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Si ma raison est peu touchante,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "C’est que mon tort n’est qu’apparent :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Je ne parle pas, moi, je chante ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Comme aux jours d’Orphée ou du Dante,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Je chante, c’est bien différent.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Si ma raison est peu touchante,\nC’est que mon tort n’est qu’apparent :\nJe ne parle pas, moi, je chante ;\nComme aux jours d’Orphée ou du Dante,\nJe chante, c’est bien différent."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Je ne parle pas, moi, Madame.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Vous voyez que je n’ai pas tort,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Je ne parle pas de ma femme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Je la chante et je clame, clame,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Je clame haut, sans crier fort.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je ne parle pas, moi, Madame.\nVous voyez que je n’ai pas tort,\nJe ne parle pas de ma femme,\nJe la chante et je clame, clame,\nJe clame haut, sans crier fort."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Je clame et vous chante à voix haute.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Qu’il plaise aux cœurs de m’épier,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Lequel pourra me prendre en faute ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Je ne compte pas sans mon hôte,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "J’écris « ne vends » sur ce papier.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je clame et vous chante à voix haute.\nQu’il plaise aux cœurs de m’épier,\nLequel pourra me prendre en faute ?\nJe ne compte pas sans mon hôte,\nJ’écris « ne vends » sur ce papier."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 12,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "J’écris à peine, je crayonne.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Je le répète encor plus haut,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Je chante et votre Âme rayonne.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Comme les lyres, je résonne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Oui… d’après La Rochefoucauld.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "J’écris à peine, je crayonne.\nJe le répète encor plus haut,\nJe chante et votre Âme rayonne.\nComme les lyres, je résonne,\nOui… d’après La Rochefoucauld."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 13,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "Ah ! Monsieur !… le duc que vous êtes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Dont la France peut se vanter,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "Fait très bien tout ce que vous faites ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "Il dit aux femmes des poëtes :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "« Libre aux vôtres de vous chanter !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ah ! Monsieur !… le duc que vous êtes,\nDont la France peut se vanter,\nFait très bien tout ce que vous faites ;\nIl dit aux femmes des poëtes :\n« Libre aux vôtres de vous chanter !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 14,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Dès qu’il ne s’agit plus de prose,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 67,
                    "line_text": "Qu’il ne s’agit plus des humains,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 68,
                    "line_text": "Au Mont où croît le Laurier-Rose,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 69,
                    "line_text": "Qu’on chante l’une ou l’autre chose,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 70,
                    "line_text": "Pour moi, je m’en lave les mains. »",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Dès qu’il ne s’agit plus de prose,\nQu’il ne s’agit plus des humains,\nAu Mont où croît le Laurier-Rose,\nQu’on chante l’une ou l’autre chose,\nPour moi, je m’en lave les mains. »"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 15,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 71,
                    "line_text": "Donc, sans épater les usages,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 72,
                    "line_text": "Je ferai, Madame, sur Vous",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 73,
                    "line_text": "Dix volumes de six cents pages,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 74,
                    "line_text": "Que je destine… pas aux sages,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 75,
                    "line_text": "Tous moins amoureux que les fous.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Donc, sans épater les usages,\nJe ferai, Madame, sur Vous\nDix volumes de six cents pages,\nQue je destine… pas aux sages,\nTous moins amoureux que les fous."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 16,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 76,
                    "line_text": "Pour terminer, une remarque,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 77,
                    "line_text": "(Si j’ose descendre à ce ton,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 78,
                    "line_text": "Madame), après, je me rembarque,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 79,
                    "line_text": "Et je vais relire Plutarque",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 80,
                    "line_text": "Dans le quartier du Panthéon :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Pour terminer, une remarque,\n(Si j’ose descendre à ce ton,\nMadame), après, je me rembarque,\nEt je vais relire Plutarque\nDans le quartier du Panthéon :"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 17,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 81,
                    "line_text": "Sans la poésie et sa flamme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 82,
                    "line_text": "(Que Vous avez, bien entendu)",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 83,
                    "line_text": "Aucun mortel, je le proclame,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 84,
                    "line_text": "N’aurait jamais connu votre âme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 85,
                    "line_text": "Rose du Paradis Perdu ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sans la poésie et sa flamme,\n(Que Vous avez, bien entendu)\nAucun mortel, je le proclame,\nN’aurait jamais connu votre âme,\nRose du Paradis Perdu ;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 18,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 86,
